headline: Advisor with $110 Million Joins Ameriprise Financial Citing Impressive Wealth Management Platform and Support Resources
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, February 03, 2025--Financial advisor Ronnie Sansom, CFP®, recently joined the independent channel of Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE: AMP) from Edward Jones with $110 million in assets. His practice is located in Andalusia, Alabama and includes Branch Administrator Karen Philpott.
